project working

00:34:18.250 --> 00:34:20.829
with the University
of Berkeley in trying

00:34:20.829 --> 00:34:23.980
to encode some languages.

00:34:23.980 --> 00:34:26.409
So I wrote them but
never heard from them.

00:34:26.409 --> 00:34:29.710
