went, he left a mark.

00:37:52.590 --> 00:37:54.750
And eventually that's
what will take off,

00:37:54.750 --> 00:37:57.440
and you will see later in
these slides that today,

00:37:57.440 --> 00:38:02.170
ADLaM is taught everywhere
across West Africa.

